    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/a2306e51f80aae88353222cf19518045.avif?t=1770144706\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras_big/a2306e51f80aae88353222cf19518045.avif?t=1770144706 width=800 height=152 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/23ef54f145b269c1ba49597299044b18.poster.avif?t=1770144706\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/23ef54f145b269c1ba49597299044b18.webm?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/23ef54f145b269c1ba49597299044b18.mp4?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>《诅咒2》</strong></i>是一款非对称多人恐怖游戏。四名幸存者须探索咒厄之地、破解谜题并逃出生天——而第五名玩家则扮演猎杀他们的致命生物。每场对局变幻莫测，充斥着紧张感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/021b013854e864d3a8b0a24fbe898b06.avif?t=1770144706\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras_big/021b013854e864d3a8b0a24fbe898b06.avif?t=1770144706 width=800 height=152 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/192ae4b80b4687960191cb1fe20bdd07.poster.avif?t=1770144706\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/192ae4b80b4687960191cb1fe20bdd07.webm?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/192ae4b80b4687960191cb1fe20bdd07.mp4?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了逃脱，幸存者必须搜寻物品、解锁房门，并完成地图各处散布的谜题。每一场对局都会将关键“钥”素重新洗牌，需要玩家快速适应。团队合作、警觉意识和沉稳操作不可或缺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/d95655aa30c4d9dfc05de051ae3f655c.avif?t=1770144706\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras_big/d95655aa30c4d9dfc05de051ae3f655c.avif?t=1770144706 width=800 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/abaf5a2c31c94675db055534afbf9ca4.poster.avif?t=1770144706\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/abaf5a2c31c94675db055534afbf9ca4.webm?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/abaf5a2c31c94675db055534afbf9ca4.mp4?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控身怀异能的恐怖生物。每种怪物皆可提供不同的游玩风格——有些潜行追踪，有些则制造混乱与迷惑。掌握其技能，将每一场对局化为心理恐怖体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/0ec0973cec6b8055574f4e2837558990.avif?t=1770144706\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras_big/0ec0973cec6b8055574f4e2837558990.avif?t=1770144706 width=800 height=152 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/90930958685043c7491d11070062ace1.poster.avif?t=1770144706\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/90930958685043c7491d11070062ace1.webm?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/90930958685043c7491d11070062ace1.mp4?t=1770144706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式视听体验：</strong>《诅咒2》使用虚幻引擎5，将图形和音频的沉浸感提升到了新的恐怖水平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式VOIP：</strong>我们的内置VOIP系统模拟了回声、混响和周围环境。不过要小心，怪物在狩猎时能听到你的声音！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>化身怪物！</strong>：在多种不同的怪物中选择一个进行游戏，惊吓你的朋友，每个怪物都有一套技能供你狩猎和消灭擅闯者。怪物亦可由AI控制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作共赢：</strong>与朋友一起游戏，最多支持5名玩家，团队合作是快速解谜与探索的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随机环境与谜题：</strong>每局游戏从不相同。每次开始新对局，钥匙、物品和谜题都会生成在不同位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义难度：</strong>在开始新对局之前选择游戏设置，自定义你想要的游戏方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221390/extras/48d4ddf2ed31f75e0ffbc8443a6bb006.avif?t=1770144706\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p></li></ul>",
